<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在离开以前，小美人鱼想见见她的家人们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，当她到王宫时，大家都睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她感到巨大的悲伤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要永远离开我的家了。”她想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我连再见也说不了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，在日出之前，她向王子王宫附近的山崖游去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爬上岩石后，小美人鱼能看见那个阳台。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一爬到海边上，她就喝了药。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她感到剧痛，剧痛使她失去了意识。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那时，她看见自己的尾巴开始裂成两半。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她醒过来，她发现自己躺在沙发上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的身上盖着一个斗篷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抬头看去，看见王子站在她身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看见你躺在岩石上。”王子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？你从哪儿来？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是你的真爱。”她想说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在海里救了你的命。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，她说不出话来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，她对王子笑，希望他能明白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说吧，别害怕。”王子温柔地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，小美人鱼只能看着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你叫什么名字？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼说不出话来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他说：“我不知道你为什么不说话，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但你还是需要我的帮助。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子帮小美人鱼站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就和海巫婆说的一样，小美人鱼每走一步，都非常痛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但在王子眼里，她看起来很完美。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们穿过大厅时，小美人鱼像云彩一样轻快地走着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你真优雅。”王子边说边带着她走进了自己的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他让他的仆人拿来一些衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把她打扮成王室的贵宾！”他命令说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他转向她温柔地问：“今天你愿意陪我参加王室的音乐会吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼期待地点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人给她穿上了一条连衣裙后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子带着她来到王宫大厅，把她介绍给了父母。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你真美！”王后感叹道说，“你从哪儿来？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，小美人鱼不能回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个高个子女人走进大厅为王子和他的父母表演。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她唱得非常甜美，王子高兴地鼓掌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼伤心地想：“我曾经唱得更甜美。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，小美人鱼听着听着，她惊讶地发现自己想跳舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抬起自己的双臂，优雅的双脚滑过地板。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼的舞蹈很迷人，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她让所有人都着了迷，特别是王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你太特别了。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会永远把你带在我身边，叫你‘我的小伙伴’。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼对王子微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的眼睛问：“这是你的承诺吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>随着时间的过去，小美人鱼变成了王子最好的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走到哪里都带着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们一起走过王宫花园，骑马穿过田野。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们一起爬上高高的山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然她不能跟他说话，但她一直微笑，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>即使她的脚疼得要命。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>